name.ja: ゴブリン<ruby>穴<rt>あな</rt></ruby><ruby>掘<rt>ほ</rt></ruby>り<ruby>隊<rt>たい</rt></ruby><ruby>長<rt>ちょう</rt></ruby>

requirement.en: If you have "The Warrior Returning Alive" or "Trap Hole" in your Graveyard, send the top card of your Deck to the Graveyard.

effect.en: 1 face-up monster on your opponent's field loses ATK equal to [the total number of "The Warrior Returning Alive" and "Trap Hole" in your Graveyard] x 1000 until the end of this turn.
